rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Rex, you should turn this down.
It's far too suspicious, I tell you.

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0002
rows.name:
It's from Chairman Bahn's Guild, and he paid
me well... I'm sure it'll be fine.

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0003
rows.name:
A high reward means
it's a dangerous job.

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0004
rows.name:
You need to think again if this is a request
you can handle.

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0005
rows.name:
It's not often I get to work alongside Drivers.
It'll be a good experience, right?

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0006
rows.name:
Gramps, you're always telling me to get
lots of different experiences.
